so in a duel i'd say a shaman gets rid of the necro anytime .<BR>
in soloing the necro is more efficient because the fear spells allows his pet to stay alive and atk while the mob is runnig . BUT the shaman is CLEARLY more powerfull for soloing . <BR>
just slow gives them that advantages . <BR>
go in sebilis ... the only class i have ever seen soloing the two froggies at entrance has always been a shaman  .lets admit it , you necros can only solos small critters , while us shamans , we can take bigger mobs , we don't have to fear them to win . <BR>
